# S05-T04: Chat Surface

## Objective
Give work-control a chat like `apps/chat`, with room for the epics right column.

## Execution
- Add a two-pane layout: left = chat thread (list + thread + `UChatPrompt`),
  right = epics column slot (filled in T06). Reuse `apps/chat` patterns (UDashboardPanel,
  UChatMessages/UChatPrompt) — copy, do not import across apps.
- Routes/pages: `chats` list + `chat/[id]` thread; persist to `wc_chats`/`wc_messages` (T03).
- This sprint the assistant reply is a stub echo; real LLM chat is S06. The point is the
  surface + persistence + the right-column mount, not conversation quality.

## Out
`apps/work-control/app/pages/chat/[id].vue`, chat composable, chat API routes

## Done when
- Can create a chat, send messages, see them persisted and reloaded on refresh.
